lles drags on and on, and we get it right off the bat, the guy's a coward. Yes, this scene is important for the big reveal at the end, but man does it go on too long. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIt's failures like the above that kept me from loving this play like I have others. It's not bad, just not brilliant. ","rating":3,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1742824?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"comedy","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1742824?shelf=comedy"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"fiction","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1742824?shelf=fiction"}},{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"play","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/1742824?shelf=play"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/285818884"},"likeCount":36,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":2,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:3965659":{"id":3965659,"__typename":"User","legacyId":3965659,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1595877858i/3965659._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":537,"viewableName":"Rachel","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/3965659-rachel","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":746},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.TCuxL3WbwNQVVjwkeNhbmw":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.TCuxL3WbwNQVVjwkeNhbmw","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.EedzMzTRY3_iT8ACzPOPPw"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:3965659"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1642902310756,"createdAt":1592006903422,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1592006916759,"text":"Helena he’s just not that into you","rating":2,"shelving":{"_